{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund more NHS support for gynaecological disorders and reduce diagnosis delays",
        "additional_details": "Thousands of women and people with gynaecological conditions wait years for diagnosis, and many suffer severe pain, fatigue, infertility and poor mental health. Delays can worsen symptoms and reduce quality of life. Faster diagnosis and better NHS treatment could prevent long-term complications and help people remain in work and education.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to fund improved NHS support for gynaecological disorders and reduced diagnosis delays.",
